videos.description: C.J. Reavis picks off J.C. Williamson's pass to halt ODU's drive.
videos.headline: Reavis's  interception stops ODU drive

videos.description: Steven Williams finds Melvin Vaughn for a 20-yard gain to put ODU in Marshall territory.
videos.headline: Williams hits  Vaughn to put ODU in Marshall territory

videos.description: Marshall's Kaare Vedvik's 27-yard field goal attempt is blocked by Bunmi Rotimi to preserve ODU's lead.
videos.headline: ODU blocks field goal attempt

videos.description: Chase Litton hits Tyre Brady for a touchdown to give Marshall the lead.
videos.headline: Litton to Brady gives Marshall the lead

videos.description: Marshall Head Coach Doc Holiday says stopping the ODU running game and getting off the field on 3rd Down are prioritizes in the second half.
videos.headline: Holiday wants improvement despite leading at the half

videos.description: Chase Litton hits Marcel Williams for a 24-yard gain that puts Marshall in ODU territory.
videos.headline: Litton to Williams puts Marshall in ODU territory

videos.description: Tyler King's 30-yard touchdown run extends Marshall's lead in the third quarter.
videos.headline: Marshall runs to a big lead

videos.description: Marshall's Chris Jackson returns a Isaiah Harper fumble 15 yards for a Marshall touchdown.
videos.headline: Marshall scores on special teams

videos.description: Chase Litton hits Ryan Yurachek for a 31-yard touchdown to extend Marshall's lead.
videos.headline: Litton's third TD pass rolls it up for Marshall

videos.description: Kaare Vedvik boots a punt from his own end zone that travels 92 yards, a Conference USA record.
videos.headline: Vedvik booms 92-yard punt
